716
00:53:38.905 --> 00:53:39.865
Baik!

717
00:53:39.865 --> 00:53:41.425
Shiba-kun, sebelah sini.

718
00:53:46.665 --> 00:53:50.045
Sakurai-san,
tolong jaga ibu dan adikku.

719
00:54:00.805 --> 00:54:03.185
Tunggu sebentar! Onii-sama!

720
00:54:07.395 --> 00:54:09.525
Ada apa, Miyuki?

721
00:54:09.525 --> 00:54:12.525
